import { Box, Grid, Paper, TextField } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

export default function BaseComponent() {
    return (
        <Box>
            <Paper>
               <Grid container>
                 <form>
                    <Grid item md>
                      search field
                      <TextField />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item>
                       button
                    </Grid>
                 </form>
               </Grid>
            </Paper>
        </Box>
    )
}
